  "body": "**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Connect device to a network that has no access to internet (or simulate poor connection in emulator)\r\n2. Login the app\r\n3. Perform manual logout\r\n4. See if user is redirected to login screen\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** endless logout. User is not redirected to login screen. Sometimes I face endless login. But endless logout is easier to reproduce as it happens every time when following the above steps. \r\n\r\n[Status-debug-logs (87).zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/files/13545527/Status-debug-logs.87.zip)\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/2d9b7d65-87bb-4194-9efa-137a53e6b07c\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** user is redirected to login screen, logout is successful. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
